Aaron Gai sg2088

To compile, do "make"

To test, follow the instuctions below:

Test 1: Basic Functionality:
./spell dictionaries/basic_dict.txt test_files/basic/simple.txt

Test 2: Punctuation Handling:
./spell dictionaries/basic_dict.txt test_files/basic/punctuation.txt

Test 3: Number Handling:
./spell dictionaries/basic_dict.txt test_files/basic/numbers.txt

Test 4: Mixed Case Test:
./spell dictionaries/case_dict.txt test_files/case_sensitivity/mixed_case.txt

Test 5: Directory Traversal (Default .txt):
./spell dictionaries/basic_dict.txt test_files/directories/

Test 6: Custom Suffix (.tst)
./spell -s .tst dictionaries/basic_dict.txt test_files/directories/

Test 7: STDIN Input
echo "hello world error" | ./spell dictionaries/basic_dict.txt